item.title: CVE-2019-1003017|2024-09-17T02:26:18.483Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20job%20import%20plugin
item.description: A data modification vulnerability exists in Jenkins Job Import Plugin 3.0 and earlier in JobImportAction.java that allows attackers to copy jobs from a preconfigured other Jenkins instance, potentially installing additional plugins necessary to load the imported job's configuration.
